                            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                            <p>Rent Direct Online Ltd are a team of people, who were left disillusioned with the current set up of the letting industry. We include tenants and landlords from all sectors: residential, commercial, property share and holiday lets. Throughout our dealings with a selection of agents in our local areas, and also of online 'Pseudo' agents we were left time and again with a bad taste in our mouths. Constant let downs, misinformation-information, deliberate lies, and lost opportunities prompted us to try to change the market and provide a better service within the industry.</p>
                            <h2>Are we a letting agency?</h2>
                            <p>No, no and no again.</p>
                            <p>Rent Direct is a sophisticated web portal offering property marketing services to private landlords. It includes some ground breaking functionality to help landlords and tenants alike easily manage their interactions in an simple, and direct manner. Cutting out the need for agencies in its entirety, while allowing for full transparency between both parties.</p>
                            <h2>So you are against the agents?</h2>
                            <p>Not at all, we respect the vast majority who offer a true service and work hard for the benefits of their clients. It's the small minority who have given the group a bad name, and necessitated the need for Rent Direct. Read our page Why No Agents? for further explanations.</p>
                            <h2>Why should I use you to show my properties. Why not stick to companies like Right Move or Zoopla or agents?</h2>
                            <p>There are several reasons why we believe you should not use the afor mentioned companies</p>
                            <div class='list-container'>
                                <ul class='custom-list'>
                                    <li>By promoting your property yourself, you are offering a unique service, providing better contact with tenants, simplified letting system, and a complete departure from traditional agency led lettings.</li>
                                    <li>The existing search aggregates only allow agents or 'Pseudo' agents to place their properties on their sites, meaning your unique property is hidden amongst 300,000 agents properties, with no clue to the average visitor that you are offering a much better experience than an agent could</li>
                                    <li>We are not competing in the same market. RightMove and Zoopla both provide an online portal to display agents properties. Taking care of the market of people who like to use the agents services. We deal fully with private landlords and tenants who for reasons of their own would prefer direct contact with the landlords.</li>
                                    <li>Letting agents charge for their services, and traditionally have an ongoing charging commitment once a tenant is found</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                           
         </div>
